Sprint: You can basically survive with any stam
Mile: 200 ~ 300
Mid: 300 ~ 500
Long: 600+

Content:
stamina stat is basically (not exactly) HP, its drained linearly from opening to middle. HP is checked on the last leg for the final spurt.
if an uma runs out of HP, they will slow down rapidly. higher speed stat requires more stamina, lower speed stat requires less

Author: genthefrog18
Content: power factors into how fast an uma can accelerate to get into their top speed, also lessens the uphill speed debuff,  it also affects how fast an uma can change lanes, which massively helps them to not be boxed in

Author: genthefrog18
Content: this means that for shorter races, since uma dont have as much time to accelerate to their top speed at each phase, power is very important

Author: genthefrog18
